VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT AllowOrigins\s*:\s*\[\]\s*string\{\s*"\*"\s*\}|AllowOrigins\s*:\s*"\*"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:AllowOriginFunc|allowedOrigins && PRESENT:AllowOrigins.*"\*"|AllowAnyOrigin
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects wildcard CORS policies in Go services.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Echo Permissive CORS.
